sequenceDiagram
  participant K as Kafka
  participant T as Transformation
  participant D as DLQ
  participant M as Monitoring
  K->>T: Deliver AP record
  T->>T: Validate vendor and GSTIN
  T-->>D: Route invalid record with ERR-MAP-003
  T-->>M: Emit data quality metric
  M-->>M: Alert if DLQ threshold exceeded

